item.description: Vienna Overview Vienna is a simple and clean blog theme for Hugo. Notable features are: Simple and clean design Client side source code highlighting Social links (Twitter, Facebook, GitHub, LinkedIn, Instagram, Keybase) Support for tags Analytics with Google Analytics or Mixpanel Responsive design Font Awesome icons Installation In your hugo site directory, run: $ mkdir themes $ cd themes $ git clone https://github.com/keichi/vienna Vienna is also included in the spf13/hugoThemes repository.
